                "invention-title": [
                    "Systematic removal method for fluorine ions in recycling process of waste lithium iron phosphate battery",
                    "废旧磷酸铁锂电池再生利用过程中氟离子的系统去除方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a systematic removal method for fluorine ions in a recycling process of a waste lithium iron phosphate battery. The system removal method comprises the following steps: carrying out electrified crushing, primary roasting and secondary roasting treatment on the waste batteries, and then sorting to obtain black powder, copper, aluminum and shell materials; placing the black powder in an alkaline solution for reaction and separation to obtain a first filtrate and a first filter residue; the first filter residues are mixed with sulfuric acid and hydrogen peroxide for acid leaching treatment, and second filtrate and second filter residues are obtained; adjusting the pH value of the second filtrate and reacting to obtain a third filtrate and a third filter residue; carrying out deep defluorination treatment on the third filtrate by adopting a defluorination agent to obtain fourth filtrate and fourth filter residues; and carrying out lithium precipitation reaction on the fourth filtrate and sodium carbonate to obtain lithium carbonate and lithium precipitation mother liquor. The system removal method for fluorine ions provided by the invention has the advantages of high fluorine removal rate, low energy consumption, low corrosion degree of fluorine to equipment and high purity of lithium carbonate products."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种废旧磷酸铁锂电池再生利用过程中氟离子的系统去除方法。所述系统去除方法包括：对废旧电池进行带电破碎、一次焙烧、二次焙烧处理，之后进行分选获得黑粉、铜、铝、外壳材料；将所述黑粉置于碱性溶液中反应并分离，获得第一滤液和第一滤渣；将所述第一滤渣与硫酸、双氧水混合进行酸浸处理，获得第二滤液和第二滤渣；调节所述第二滤液的pH值并反应，获得第三滤液和第三滤渣；采用除氟剂对所述第三滤液进行深度除氟处理获得第四滤液和第四滤渣；将所述第四滤液与碳酸钠进行沉锂反应，获得碳酸锂和沉锂母液。本发明提供的氟离子的系统去除方法氟去除率高、能耗低、氟对设备腐蚀程度低、碳酸锂产品纯度高。"
                }
            ]
